   290→															You've created{" "}
   291→															{formatArtifactCount(standards, skills)}.
   292→															Centralize, govern and distribute your AI agent
   293→															playbook at scale with Packmind.
   294→														</p>
   295→														<div className="flex gap-2 mt-2">
   296→															<a
   297→																href="https://packmind.com"
   298→																target="_blank"
   299→																rel="noopener noreferrer"
   300→																className="btn-secondary text-xs py-1 px-2"
   301→															>
   302→																packmind.com
   303→															</a>
   304→															<button
   305→																onClick={() => setShowTourModal(true)}
   306→																className="btn-primary text-xs py-1 px-2"
